OL,3,CNo 10 cannot block release of
OL,4,CMandelson documents, officials say
OL,6,FNo 10 will be unable to block the
OL,7,Fpublication of documents relating to
OL,8,FLord Peter Mandelson's appointment as
OL,9,Fambassador to the US, with
OL,10,FParliament's security watchdog having
OL,11,Fthe final say.
OL,13,FThe decision follows a parliamentary
OL,14,Forder for the government to release a
OL,15,Fhuge quantity of documents relating to
OL,16,Fthe 2024 appointment of Mandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
