CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772197440
OL,3,CNo 10 cannot block release of
OL,4,CMandelson documents, officials say
OL,6,FThe government has come under fire
OL,7,Fover what was known, and when, about
OL,8,FMandelson's links to the late
OL,9,Fpaedophile financier Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,10,FQuestions have also been raised about
OL,11,Fthe peer's vetting process.
OL,13,FIn a statement on Thursday,
OL,14,FParliament's Intelligence and Security
OL,15,FCommittee (ISC) said officials had
OL,16,Fconfirmed "in writing" that it would
OL,17,Fhave the final say on which papers
OL,18,Fwould be released.
OL,26,@xD@KOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
