OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772197440
OL,3,CNo 10 cannot block release of
OL,4,CMandelson documents, officials say
OL,6,FSome of the thousands of documents are
OL,7,Fexpected to be withheld for national
OL,8,Fsecurity or foreign relations reasons,
OL,9,Fbut it will be up to the ISC, rather
OL,10,Fthan ministers, to determine which
OL,11,Fitems should be redacted.
OL,13,FThe ISC statement added: "The Prime
OL,14,FMinister ` or anyone else in
OL,15,FGovernment ` will not be able to
OL,16,Foverrule the Committee's decision to
OL,17,Fpublish material that has been
OL,18,Freferred to it."
OL,26,@zD@PO]
