OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772197440
OL,3,CNo 10 cannot block release of
OL,4,CMandelson documents, officials say
OL,6,FControl over which files to withhold
OL,7,Fwas given to the parliamentary
OL,8,Fcommittee after a Downing Street
OL,9,Fclimbdown in the face of a Labour
OL,10,Fbacklash against initial plans for the
OL,11,FCabinet Secretary to make the judgment.
OL,13,FThe first tranche of documents is
OL,14,Funlikely to be published next week,
OL,15,Fand more likely in the following week,
OL,16,Fit is understood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
