OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772197440
OL,3,CNo 10 cannot block release of
OL,4,CMandelson documents, officials say
OL,6,FThey are expected to include messages
OL,7,Fbetween ministers and senior officials
OL,8,Fthat have the potential to prove
OL,9,Fembarrassing for the government and
OL,10,Feven raise tensions with Donald
OL,11,FTrump's White House.
OL,13,FISC chairman Lord Beamish has
OL,14,Fpreviously said that "embarrassment
OL,15,Fisn't a reason for withholding
OL,16,Finformation".
OL,26,@vD@VOUxD@LO]
