OL,3,CNo 10 cannot block release of
OL,4,CMandelson documents, officials say
OL,6,FThe government has also agreed a
OL,7,Fframework with the Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Fon which documents can be released
OL,9,Fwithout prejudicing the ongoing police
OL,10,Finvestigation, according to the ISC.
OL,12,FLord Mandelson was arrested on Monday
OL,13,Fon suspicion of misconduct in public
OL,14,Foffice, having been accused of passing
OL,15,Fsensitive information on to Epstein
OL,16,Fduring his time as business secretary.
OL,17,FHe has been bailed until May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
